```plantuml
@startuml vectranetworks_AWS-Traffic-Mirroring-Session-Manager

actor User

participant "tap.py" as Tap
participant "config_vpc.py" as ConfigVPC
participant "ec2_api_client.py" as EC2ApiClient
participant "spile_tapper.py" as SpileTapper
participant "spile.py" as Spile
participant "blacklist.py" as Blacklist
participant "whitelist.py" as Whitelist
participant "nlb_factory.py" as NlbFactory
participant "nlb_target_factory.py" as NlbTargetFactory

User -> Tap: Run tap.py
Tap -> ConfigVPC: Load VPC Configurations
ConfigVPC -> EC2ApiClient: Fetch VPC Data
EC2ApiClient --> ConfigVPC: Return VPC Data
Tap -> SpileTapper: Discover Instances
SpileTapper -> EC2ApiClient: List Nitro EC2 Instances
EC2ApiClient --> SpileTapper: Return Instance List
SpileTapper -> Blacklist: Check Instance Blacklist
Blacklist --> SpileTapper: Blacklist Status
SpileTapper -> Whitelist: Check Instance Whitelist
Whitelist --> SpileTapper: Whitelist Status

alt Instance Eligible
    SpileTapper -> Spile: Manage Sessions
    Spile -> EC2ApiClient: Create Traffic Mirroring Session
    Spile -> NlbTargetFactory: Create Mirror Target
    NlbTargetFactory -> NlbFactory: Create NLB
    NlbFactory --> NlbTargetFactory: Return NLB
    NlbTargetFactory --> Spile: Return Mirror Target
    Spile --> SpileTapper: Session Managed
end

Tap -> Tap: Iterate Next VPC

@enduml
```